Package org.gradle.tooling.connection

The main interfaces and classes to create composite Gradle connections.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    FailedModelResult<T>
    The result of a failed model request.
    GradleConnection
    Represents a connection to a composite Gradle build.
    GradleConnectionBuilder
    Builds a new composite Gradle connection.
    GradleConnectionBuilder.ParticipantBuilder
    Builds a new participant that will be included in the connection.
    ModelResult<T>
    The result of a model request.
    ModelResults<T>
    A set of model results for multiple projects.
